message.body: I didn't understand that Zoe's show was at haverford and your show!! I thought you meant your music stuff...I was so confused! So of course you'll be there! I only figured that out once I ran into Gavi at buffalo exchange and she was flyering for you
I don't like her work (just not my thang) but I really really like HER! She lied and told nam I made a great cappuccino (I did not) and I will always be thankful
